The classification toolbox is a Matlab toolbox that can be used in conjunction with the FieldTrip toolbox for MEG and EEG analysis. It is being developed at the Intelligent Systems Group at the Institute for Computing and Inforamtion Science and at the Donders Centre for Cognitive Neuroimaging (DCCN).

